{"name":"Grilled Caesar Salad","slug":"grilled-caesar-salad","description":"Grilling a Caesar salad adds smoky flavour to a classic, elevating taste and texture. Grill a double batch of chicken so you have leftovers for another meal.","ingredients":[{"name":"boneless, skinless chicken breasts","quantity":"1 lb (450 g)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"oil","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Rotisserie Chicken Seasoning","quantity":"1 pkg","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"large head romaine lettuce","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Sea Salt","quantity":null,"additionalInstruction":"optional, to taste"},{"name":"Black Pepper","quantity":null,"additionalInstruction":"optional, to taste"},{"name":"Caesar Dressing","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":"prepared"},{"name":"Caesar Dressing Mix","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"light mayonnaise or Greek yogurt","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"lemon juice","quantity":"1 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"olive oil","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"milk, your choice","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"crushed garlic cloves","quantity":"2","additionalInstruction":"optional"},{"name":"shaved Parmesan cheese","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"croutons ","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"20 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":["Preheat grill to medium-high.","Rub chicken with oil. Shake seasoning on both sides.","Grill, with lid closed, 4–5 min per side, or until cooked through. Remove from grill and set aside; cover to keep warm.","Lower grill to medium heat.","Wash lettuce and quarter lengthwise, leaving the stem intact. Season with salt and pepper, if desired.","Cook wedges, cut-